OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTaliban leader orders      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FSharia law punishments     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Taliban leader Haibatullah Akhundzada  
OL,6, has ordered Afghan judges to impose    
OL,7, punishments for certain crimes that may
OL,8, include public amputations and stoning.
OL,10,FHis spokesman said offences such as    
OL,11,Frobbery, kidnapping and sedition must  
OL,12,Fbe punished in line with the group's   
OL,13,Finterpretation of Islamic Sharia law.  
OL,15,FWhen in power in the 1990s, the Taliban
OL,16,Fwere condemned for such punishments,   
OL,17,Fwhich included public executions.      
OL,19,FThey promised to rule more moderately  
OL,20,Fwhen they retook power last year.      
